26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-13T20:54:44+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>b8bb5be9f3a02d15dec136a4fac82f92</id><title>當年藍灣半島政府救咗信和一次，今日信和投桃報李</title><updated>2025-08-14T01:21:10+08:00</updated><author><name>hkduck123</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T01:21:10+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573591566"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573591566"&gt;信和為咗答謝政府，自己mark高個價投屯門地皮，報答左你啦，今次大家互不相欠&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32006690&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T01:21:10+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>3b19d81bd0abbff6f16b9cf06a39994b</id><title>金管局買入近34億港元 銀行結餘將跌穿550億元</title><updated>2025-08-14T11:04:35+08:00</updated><author><name>驚青猛男</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T11:04:35+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573594824"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573594824"&gt;金管局買入近34億港元銀行結餘將跌穿550億元&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;港匯偏弱，觸發7.85兌1美元的弱方兌換保證。金管局在紐約時段買入33.76億港元，沽出美元。明日本港銀行體系總結餘將降至537.16億港元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1818078-20250814.htm?spTabChangeable=0" target="_blank" uhash="506d1604d55210171a9a672c7e84e830"&gt;https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1818078-20250814.htm?spTabChangeable=0&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32006961&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T11:04:35+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>ad4579866928e75a6dac94c5306f0e4f</id><title>湯文亮：炒家套戥或得不償失</title><updated>2025-08-14T11:43:48+08:00</updated><author><name>好久冇見</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T11:43:48+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595355"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595355"&gt;湯文亮：炒家套戥或得不償失&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;【明報專訊】星期三早上去到茶餐廳，見到有很多客人食完早餐之後用500元紙幣找數，收銀機本來有價值數千元的100元紙幣，但找下找下，已經所餘無幾，有客人擔心自己用500元埋單，老闆無得找續，於是打算離開。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e7%b6%93%e6%bf%9f/article/20250814/s00004/1755102880297" target="_blank" uhash="a744fa8903f9d8cfadabdf8d40551f80"&gt;https://news.mingpao.com/pns/經濟/article/20250814/s00004/1755102880297&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32006995&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T11:43:48+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>a0874d5c43ea2b41c9e6fe931d350990</id><title>如果同銀行做按揭，但變左負資產，即時用現金還晒d按揭,係米吾使罰息同吾會比銀行收樓?//</title><updated>2025-08-14T11:59:03+08:00</updated><author><name>leonleon622</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T11:59:03+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595532"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595532"&gt;如果同銀行做按揭，但變左負資產，即時用現金還晒d按揭,係米吾使罰息同吾會比銀行收樓?//&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007002&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T11:59:03+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>2c021255d1ad5db37d583df694fc8547</id><title>馬鞍山私樓3房 呎價低於9000元成交</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:00:10+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:00:10+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595548"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595548"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3992342%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E9%259E%258D%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E7%25A7%2581%25E6%25A8%25933%25E6%2588%25BF%25C2%25A0%2520%25E5%2591%258E%25E5%2583%25B9%25E4%25BD%258E%25E6%2596%25BC9000%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=26f74b2fabfa094a9e8759b2a6a93e4c&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3992 ... 低於9000元成交?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;私樓成交&lt;br/&gt;撰文：陳嘉敏&lt;br/&gt;發布時間：2025/08/12 19:49&lt;br/&gt;馬鞍山私樓3房呎價低於9000元成交&lt;br/&gt;▲ 馬鞍山私樓3房呎價低於9000元成交&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;世紀21奇豐物業天宇海分行經理黃宗信表示，該行新近錄得馬鞍山翠擁華庭10座低層B室成交，實用面積765平方呎，3房2廳，向南望山景，成交價685萬元，實用呎價8,954元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原業主於1999年4月購入上述單位，當時作價364萬元，持貨26年至今沽售，帳面獲利321萬元，單位期內樓價升88%。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007003&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T12:00:10+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>99a5216be6940b15b2e58646d998a914</id><title>🆘迎海‧星灣御四房戶獲回流客1998萬購入 原業主12年蝕517萬</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:00:41+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:00:41+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595557"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595557"&gt;美聯楊震霆表示，馬鞍山迎海‧星灣御25座高層A室，實用面積約1,390方呎，四房設計，以2,280萬元放售，議價後以1,998萬元成交，呎價約14,374元。買家於外地準備回流，特意返港買樓，原業主則持貨12年帳面虧損約517萬元。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：迎海‧星灣御四房戶獲回流客1998萬購入原業主12年蝕517萬 | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250812%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250812213148500-0812_00842_001.html%3Fkeywordid%3D4028828d7471d2a50174ba053e176f16%26keywordname%3D%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=a4a3dcd5443b033bc2a7efd4d5079355&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/fina ... &amp;amp;amp;keywordname=地產&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007005&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T12:00:41+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>9f285d07d01bbe8e664ed3aef709f09b</id><title>🆘🆘土瓜灣喜點跌穿10年前一手買價 較高位冧35%</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:01:21+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:01:21+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595562"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595562"&gt;二手樓價尋底。利嘉閣林玉燕表示，土瓜灣喜點高層G室，實用面積約259方呎，為開放式間隔，區內買家睇樓一次，即以380萬港元購入，呎價約14,672元。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據悉，原業主於2015年以約412.8萬元一手購入，約10年帳面蝕讓32.8萬元，貶值約7.9%。資料顯示，同室較低層單位，2018年最高曾以585萬元登記售出，樓價高位回落約35%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：土瓜灣喜點跌穿10年前一手買價較高位冧35% | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250813%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250813172018371-0813_00842_001.html%3Fkeywordid%3D4028828d7471d2a50174ba053e176f16%26keywordname%3D%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=9780e1f7559b6123aab1914d58d61879&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/fina ... &amp;amp;amp;keywordname=地產&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007006&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T12:01:21+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>390b116721ffde8bc50b26e4cbd0af68</id><title>🆘🆘長沙灣喜遇百分百蝕讓！一房406萬蝕沽 8年帳面貶值逾一成半</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:01:45+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:01:45+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595568"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595568"&gt;二手市場疲弱，長沙灣半新盤喜遇近年二手成交個案均告蝕讓收場，最新有一房戶以406萬元蝕沽，單位8年帳面貶值逾一成半。翻查資料，如連同今次成交，喜遇今年暫錄6宗二手成交，全數均需蝕讓，最勁一宗帳面輸23%。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;一房406萬沽上手8年蒸發76萬&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;香港置業分行區域董事方文偉表示，是次成交單位為喜遇中層F室，實用面積約298平方呎，屬一房間隔，座向北。單位最初430萬元叫價放盤，約數月後獲外區客接洽，雙方經議價後以約406萬元沽出，呎價約13,624元。至於，新買家為首置客，因鍾情主人房大，故睇2次樓後決定入市。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;據知，原業主於2017年10月以約482萬元購入單位，持貨約8年，是次轉手帳面蝕讓約76萬元，單位期內貶值15.8%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;百分百蝕讓最勁輸逾兩成&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;翻查成交資料，如連同上述成交，喜遇年初至今共錄6宗二手成交，當作全數均需蝕讓，蝕幅8%至23%。當中最勁一宗蝕讓為一夥中層F室一房，實用面積約298平方呎，原業主持貨8年以388萬元沽出，帳面勁蝕逾115萬元或近23%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址: 長沙灣喜遇百分百蝕讓！一房406萬蝕沽8年帳面貶值逾一成半 | 香港01 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F60266145%3Futm_source%3D01articlecopy%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=ddbeb390aa42ff4ea1f2b070a6f53b94&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.hk01.com/article/602 ... utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007007&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T12:01:45+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>439e0fa026c01e55a64818edfd704d46</id><title>🆘🆘直擊單位｜滙景花園3房小海景賣880萬 回到10年前跌價2%</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:02:23+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:02:23+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595580"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595580"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3992913%2F%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%2596%25AE%25E4%25BD%258D%25EF%25BD%259C%25E6%25BB%2599%25E6%2599%25AF%25E8%258A%25B1%25E5%259C%25923%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%2599%25AF%25E8%25B3%25A3880%25E8%2590%25AC%2520%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%2588%25B010%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2589%258D%25E8%25B7%258C%25E5%2583%25B92-%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=69d56de61bd173a59f8aea7f665a3839&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3992 ... 到10年前跌價2-?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;港鐵藍田站滙景花園有持貨10年業主，帳面微蝕離場。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;市場消息指，17座低層E室，實用720平方呎，屬套3房戶型，外望小海景，最新以880萬元易手，呎價12,222元。較上星期17座高層H室，同呎價，享開揚海景，以890萬元成交。最新成交價僅低10萬元，故屬理想水平。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;▼點擊圖片放大&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;+4&lt;br/&gt;原業主於2015年以898萬元購入，持貨10年，帳面損失18萬元或2%。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007008&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T12:02:23+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>d5b79640efabcb8fa9a8a4ccbc2ba210</id><title>請驗樓師驗收惠州新盤遭多名保安恐嚇！😱😱😱難怪不少內地人都寧可來港置業</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:24:16+08:00</updated><author><name>stoddort</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:24:16+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595811"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595811"&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #0000ff; "&gt;好多年過30嘅廢中佬冇本事買香港樓&lt;img alt="" border="0" smilieid="9" src="https://www.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default2/titter.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="font-weight: bold;"&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span style="color: #0000ff; "&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=3434944" target="_blank"&gt;@~kurapika~&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7321592" target="_blank"&gt;@過去深愛的羊腩&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7333091" target="_blank"&gt;@vovovo.N&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7256576" target="_blank"&gt;@叔叔要不要&lt;/a&gt;分身Account&lt;a class="usertag" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=3395993" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span uid="3395993"&gt;@Youngbro&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7327835" target="_blank"&gt;@買樓唔好搞阿叔&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=6673014" target="_blank"&gt;@袋中紅色主題&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=6577149" target="_blank"&gt;@車站宇宙的婆仔&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=4338023" target="_blank"&gt;@smart004&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7320360" target="_blank"&gt;@新窮A&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="usertag" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=3697327" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span uid="3697327"&gt;@hkduck123&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="usertag" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=5503647" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span uid="5503647"&gt;@931931&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="usertag" href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/space.php?uid=7348949" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;span uid="7348949"&gt;@johnlamAust2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/120825_169_iet_fish__v1_1024.jpg" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/120825_169_iet_fish__v1_1024.jpg" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/2b6ffd/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/120825_169_iet_fish__v1_1024.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;▲網絡熱話｜本港年輕情侶請驗樓師驗收惠州新盤遭多名保安恐嚇！ 網民：唔敢想像入去住之後有咩事發生&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;隨著近年中港加快融合，不少港人均於內地置業。日前有一對95後香港情侶於抖音上載影片；指自己早前購入惠州星河冠譽府一夥3房單位，並於日前前赴惠州收樓，並請來驗樓師幫忙驗收單位。惟驗收期間，一名身穿紅色上衣的男子及屋苑多名保安上門，恐嚇業主及該名驗樓師，最終更需請公安上門處理。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121615_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121615_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/aabd54/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121615_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121620_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121620_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/f3ddab/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121620_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121629_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121629_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/652d67/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121629_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;女事主對相關行為感到憤怒，直言自己合法合規地請驗樓師上門驗收單位，卻被多名人士上門欺負及恐嚇，認為相當恐怖，亦反問現時聘用驗樓師驗樓是否犯法。驗樓師更向他們反映，要不是兩名業主在場，可能已被抓至後樓梯打了。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121842_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121842_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/3d65e7/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121842_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121904_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121904_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/e8d689/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121904_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span class="post-img-container" data-pid="573595811" original-img="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121908_300.png" style='\"display:block\"'&gt;&lt;img border="0" data-src="https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121908_300.png" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/63b124/f/800x0/https://static04.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/3990000/3992063/Screenshot2025-08-11121908_300.png"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;相關片段日前被轉載至本港討論區，有網民直言，「驗樓都咁誇張，唔敢諗入去 (住) 之後有咩事發生」，「未入伙已食鐵拳」；故難怪不少內地人都寧可來港置業，皆因「起碼法律保障及管理好過大陸N倍」。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007022&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T12:24:16+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>aba00f9ca1e5511cb1c6a6f11aedc1c2</id><title>🔥🔥🔥收租廠佬大受刺激！以全蝕姿態連沽各區8住宅 平均虧近3成😆😆😆</title><updated>2025-08-14T12:25:35+08:00</updated><author><name>johnlamAust2</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-08-14T12:25:35+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573595826"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573595826"&gt;&lt;div class="embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9"&gt;&lt;iframe allowfullscreen="" class="embed-responsive-item" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YwCcKXURXro?wmode=transparent" wmode="Opaque"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://youtu.be/YwCcKXURXro?si=f1DtNjyHM3jTu30G" target="_blank"&gt;https://youtu.be/YwCcKXURXro?si=f1DtNjyHM3jTu30G&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a class="postmorevideochannel" href="videochannel.php" title="進入香討影片區"&gt;進入香討影片區&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=32007023&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1073269579689d67f728e704_82296737"/><published>2025-08-14T12:25:35+08:00</published></entry></feed>